{"word":"G3433 - μόλις - mólis - mol'-is - Hardly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μόλις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mólis</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mol'-is</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hardly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அரிதாய், வருத்தத்தோடு - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. with difficulty, hardly"},{"paragraph":"2. not easily, scarcely, very rarely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably by a variation for <a href=\"#/G3425 - μόγις - mógis - mog'-is/3425\">G3425</a>; <i>with difficulty:</i> - hardly, scarce (-ly), + with much work.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3425/3425\">G3425</a>, <a href=\"#/G3433/3433\">G3433</a>"}]}